<hymn_number>82</hymn_number>
<title>He, Zaza mahasambatra FFPM82</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 He, Zaza mahasambatra
 No omena ho antsika !
 Virjina no niteraka
 Ilay Andriantsika
 Izay Zanak'Andriamanitra.

[V2]
 Nandao ny voninahitra
 Hanavotra ny very ;
 Ka saotra no aterinay,
 Ry Jeso Kristy Tomponay,
 Mpamonjy manan-kery !</lyrics>
</song>